name: Felicia De Maio

name: Lakshmi P
text: Good and fast service. Love the seasonal specials. Recently tried the popper pizza and the breaded chicken wings. Both were amazing. The wings with the ranch was an amazing combo. The pizza is cheesy and the crust was really good

text: Terrible customer service! I had to repeat 5 times my credit card number to this guy and he idiotically kept saying " what was the number of the credit card." So I don't think Pizza Hut needed a better location, what they really need is better employees.
